error codes! 

0 : no error
1 : email address is already in use ( email must be unique in the database)
2 : password does not meet the requirements (it must have more then 5 characters)
3 : Wrong activation code. I valid activation code is needed to activate an accound 
4 : not all required fields in the body where available
5 : The activation code is valid but was already used
6 : the request was made with an invalid token or a ID/Token mismatch 
7 : This token has only reading rights, this action cannot be performed with this token
8 : not a valid action 